Hi Ava ,

Thank you so much for sending through the updates.

Website Update Requests
1. Home Page



  • In the carousel, please link "Compressive Shop Drawings - Send Us Your Plans" to the following URL:
    https://duracube.com.au/send-us-your-plans/



2. Colours Page



  • Please replace the existing colour images with the images provided in this file:
    https://drive.google.com/file/d/16l5wTKXrs-ZdDZKX9D2gcS4_KsSGd0em/view?usp=sharing



  • At the bottom of the page, update the "Download Spec Exclusive" button to link to:
    https://duracube.com.au/login/



3. Page Alignment / Pop-Up Behaviour - Toliet Partition Pricing



  • Following team review, some page elements and text appear misaligned.



  • Would it be possible to convert this section into a pop-up that appears when the page loads, then disappears, while keeping all other updates as they are?






4. Interactive Gallery Page Development

As the provided file did not include all states and colours, some options are not currently appearing on the filter section of the page.

Could you please check this and ensure the gallery is easy for us to edit internally, similar to our case study pages for addition of more images and filter section items ?

Additionally, when an image is selected, it currently zooms into the image. Please remove this zoom interaction.

Please let me know if any further clarification is required.
Priority attention is required for the Home Page and Colours Page. The remaining items can be addressed afterward.

Kind Regards,

Nidhi Toppo
Marketing Coordinator

1300 387 228
